                        <p>A group of
                            <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101128T092549-0500"?>I<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101128T092548-0500" content="i"?>nternet
                            users 50-65 years of age were randomly chosen and asked to report the
